            >
              <Icon name="ri:qq-line" class="w-4 h-4" />
              <span>QQ</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 mb-4">
            Hello! I'm Shin, a CTF cryptographer who focuses on
            exploring, learning, and researching cryptographic problems.
            Welcome to contact me to exchange friend links {'(∠・ω< )⌒★'}
          </p>
          <img src="https://ooo.0x0.ooo/2024/03/21/Ogesfb.jpg" alt="1685637181469" style="zoom:30%;" />
